node.text:
10 Instagram Story Ideas you need to try! 

☁️ Repost your TikTok to your story!
☁️ Inspirational Quotes/Daily Motivation
☁️ Mini Vlog of your morning
☁️ Show off the recent project you’re working on
☁️ Add a poll & ask your audience a question
☁️ Your current Amazon Faves 
☁️ Your go-to lunch order 
☁️ Cross off your to-do list! 
☁️ This-or-That Instagram Poll
☁️ Show us a tbt! 

IG stories are the best way to connect with your audience & show your personality 🤍 

Save this post for some inspo whenever you’re stuck for an idea🤍
